{"id":"e37f1d0b-fb84-4b91-b3c8-d02787dc50d9","name":"Teen Titans and Young Justice","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(92, 158, 229)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">The idea for this bot came to me spontaneously. If you think about it that way, it's a melding of different canons and universes. It's basically taken from the Young Justice cartoon series, but with a different cast of characters.</mark></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(92, 158, 229)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">In the canon of this bot, the Teen Titans used to be the first generation of Young Justice, and then they took over the next generation.</mark></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(92, 158, 229)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">The Teen Titans line-up (they mentor Young Justice) consists of:</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(69, 114, 202)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Dick Grayson/Nightwing</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(69, 114, 202)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Princess Coriand'r/Starfire</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(69, 114, 202)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Rachel Roth/Raven</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(69, 114, 202)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Victor Stone/Cyborg</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(69, 114, 202)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Garfield Logan/Beastboy</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(69, 114, 202)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Donna Troy/Wonder Girl</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(69, 114, 202)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Wally West/Flash</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(69, 114, 202)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Roy Harper/Arsenal</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(69, 114, 202)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Kaldur'Ahm/Aqualad</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: #a21313\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">The Young Justice team consists of:</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 220, 153)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Timothy Drake/Red Robin</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 220, 153)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Conner Kent/Superboy</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 220, 153)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Bart Allen/Impulse</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 220, 153)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Cassandra Sandsmark/Wonder Girl</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 220, 153)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Greta Hayes/Secret</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 220, 153)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Lian Harper/Cheshire Cat.</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 220, 153)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">This is more of my rambling headcanon from a bad fanfic, but hope you enjoy it</mark></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 220, 153)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">(This bot is also made with another bot, so post if there are any mistakes)</mark></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"WHc8pFxLtBF2OqxXAmNE6.webp","creator":"Bridget20.0","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🦸 Hero","🦄 Non-human","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":1062,"messages":34176,"created_at":"2025-06-02T18:49:40.201815+00:00"}